<table width=600 align=left><tr><td width=600>
<img src="mena.gif" alt="Middle East Map" width=381 height=164 align=left USEMAP="#mena" border=0>
<font face="arial" size=-1>
<p>The Middle East and North Africa are fertile grounds for human rights violations.  Real democracies exist in a minority of
countries, while some still subsist under brutal dictatorships.  <br clear="all">
<blockquote><blockquote><p>
The rights of religious and ethnic minorities are often
compromised, and the struggle between religious fanatics and government repressors have often lead to the suffering of many
innocent victims.  Freedom of speech is greatly curtailed, and human rights NGOs and journalists operate under danger of
arrests and lawsuits.  
</font></blockquote></blockquote>
</td></tr></table>



<br clear="all">
